<article id="post-224" class="post-224 post type-post status-publish format-standard hentry category-anomalycon-2015">
	<header class="entry-header">
		
		<h2 class="entry-title"><a href="https://www.anomalycon.com/anomalycon-2015/its-alive/" rel="bookmark">It&#8217;s ALIVE!</a></h2>	</header><!-- .entry-header -->

	
	
	<div class="entry-content">
		<p>GREETINGS EVERYONE!</p>
<p>Today is the day, and AnomalyCon is now in session!</p>
<p>Some quick reminders for all of you:<br />
REGISTRATION will be OPEN on site:<br />
FOR PREREG starting at 1pm Friday.<br />
Friday: 2:00 PM until 8:00 PM<br />
 Saturday: 9:00 AM until 8:00 PM<br />
 Sunday: 9:00 AM until 6PM<br />
Registration ON SITE is $35 for the weekend, or $15 for Fri or Sun and $20 for Sat. Children under 8 are free and ages 8-13 are half price.</p>
<p>VENDOR ROOM and ART GALLERY hours:<br />
Fri: 5p-9p<br />
Sat: 10a-8p<br />
Sun: 10a-4p<br />
NO admittance to the vendor&#8217;s room without a badge.</p>
	</div><!-- .entry-content -->

	<footer class="entry-footer">
		<span class="byline"><span class="author vcard"><span class="screen-reader-text">Author </span> <a class="url fn n" href="https://www.anomalycon.com/author/curucar/">Curucar</a></span></span><span class="posted-on"><span class="screen-reader-text">Posted on </span><a href="https://www.anomalycon.com/anomalycon-2015/its-alive/" rel="bookmark"><time class="entry-date published" datetime="2015-03-27T05:10:27+00:00">March 27, 2015</time><time class="updated" datetime="2016-03-30T18:09:54+00:00">March 30, 2016</time></a></span><span class="cat-links"><span class="screen-reader-text">Categories </span><a href="https://www.anomalycon.com/category/anomalycon-2015/" rel="category tag">AnomalyCon 2015</a></span>			</footer><!-- .entry-footer -->
